### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@authToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###Recuperar todos los ticketTypes (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/ticketType
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Crear un ticketType con modo SCHEDULED (programado)
# @name createScheduledTicketType
POST {{baseUrl}}/ticketType
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "ticketTypeName": "Early Bird",
    "beginDatetime": "2026-01-20 00:00:00",
    "finishDatetime": "2026-02-15 23:59:59",
    "price": 3500,
    "maxQuantity": 100,
    "event": 1,
    "saleMode": "scheduled"
}

### Crear un ticketType con modo MANUAL
# @name createManualTicketType
POST {{baseUrl}}/ticketType
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "ticketTypeName": "VIP Manual",
    "price": 5000,
    "maxQuantity": 50,
    "event": 1,
    "saleMode": "manual",
    "isManuallyActivated": false
}

### ID del ticket type creado
@ticketTypeId = {{createManualTicketType.response.body.data.id}}

### Obtener un ticketType por id
GET {{baseUrl}}/ticketType/{{ticketTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Activar venta manualmente (usando PATCH normal)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/ticketType/{{ticketTypeId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "isManuallyActivated": true
}

### Desactivar venta manualmente
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/ticketType/{{ticketTypeId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "isManuallyActivated": false
}

### Cambiar de modo manual a scheduled
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/ticketType/{{ticketTypeId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "saleMode": "scheduled",
    "beginDatetime": "2026-01-20 00:00:00",
    "finishDatetime": "2026-03-01 23:59:59"
}

### Actualizar fechas de un ticketType scheduled
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/ticketType/{{ticketTypeId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "beginDatetime": "2026-01-25 00:00:00",
    "finishDatetime": "2026-02-28 23:59:59"
}

### Eliminar un ticketType
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/ticketType/{{ticketTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
